==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Hellenic
<hw>Hel*len"ic</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The dialect, formed with slight
variations from the Attic, which prevailed among Greek writers after the
time of Alexander.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hellenism</ent>⟦br⟧
